#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&bovo; is a Gomoku (from Japanese <foreignphrase lang=\"ja\">五目並べ</"
"foreignphrase>, <quote>five points</quote>) like game for two players, where "
"the opponents alternate in placing their respective pictogram on the game "
"board. The aim of this game is to connect five of your own pieces in an "
"unbroken row vertically, horizontally or diagonally."
msgstr ""
"&bovo; je Gomoku (iz japonščine <foreignphrase lang=\"ja\">五目並べ</"
"foreignphrase>, <quote>pet točk</quote>), podobna igra za dva igralca, kjer "
"nasprotnika izmenično postavljata svoj piktogram na igralno ploščo. Cilj te "
"igre je povezati pet svojih kosov v neprekinjeno vrsto navpično, vodoravno "
"ali diagonalno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71 index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "Opomba:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also known as: Connect Five, Five in a row, X and O, Noughts and Crosses"
msgstr "Znana tudi kot: Poveži pet, Pet v vrsto, X in O, krožci in križci"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "&bovo; main screen"
msgstr "&bovo; glavni zaslon"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connect five of your own pieces in an unbroken row vertically, horizontally "
"or diagonally."
msgstr ""
"Povežite pet svojih kosov v neprekinjeno vrsto navpično, vodoravno ali "
"diagonalno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first time &bovo; is started it is launched in demo mode where two AI "
"players battle each other. You can always start a new game using the "
"<guibutton>New</guibutton> button on the toolbar, the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu entry on the menubar or using the default shortcut "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Prvič &bovo; se začne se zažene v predstavitvenem načinu, kjer se dva "
"igralca AI borita drug z drugim. Novo igro lahko vedno začnete z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Novo</guibutton> v orodni vrstici, menijskim vnosom "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> na menijsko vrstico ali uporabo privzete bližnjice <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because the first player always has an advantage over the second player, "
"&bovo; will alternate the players, switching them every new game."
msgstr ""
"Ker ima prvi igralec vedno prednost pred drugim, bo &bovo; zamenjal igralce "
"vsako novo igro."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are the first player - start the game by placing your pictogram "
"anywhere on the playing field. If you are the second player wait until the "
"first player places the pictogram and then do the same yourself. You can "
"place your mark into any square on the field, unless it’s already occupied "
"by another game piece (regardless of whether it’s your pictogram or that of "
"your opponent’s)."
msgstr ""
"Če ste prvi igralec - začnite igro tako, da svoj piktogram postavite kamor "
"koli na igralno polje. Če ste drugi igralec, počakajte, da prvi igralec "
"postavi piktogram, in nato storite isto. Svojo oznako lahko postavite na "
"poljubno polje na igrišču, razen če je že zasedeno z drugo igralno figuro "
"(ne glede na to, ali je to vaš piktogram ali piktogram vašega nasprotnika)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have to place your pieces in a way that prevents your opponent from "
"connecting five marks in an unbroken row vertically, horizontally or "
"diagonally. In the same time you have to connect five of your own pieces in "
"an unbroken row vertically, horizontally or diagonally. Whoever succeeds in "
"doing so first – wins the round."
msgstr ""
"Svoje figure morate postaviti tako, da nasprotniku preprečite, da bi povezal "
"pet točk v neprekinjeno vrsto navpično, vodoravno ali diagonalno. Istočasno "
"morate povezati pet svojih kosov v neprekinjeno vrsto navpično, vodoravno "
"ali diagonalno. Komur to uspe prvemu – zmaga krog."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules"
msgstr "Pravila igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players take turn to place their respective marks on the playing board."
msgstr "Igralci izmenično postavljajo svoje oznake na igralno ploščo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A player cannot move their already placed mark or put their mark upon an "
"already placed mark."
msgstr ""
"Igralec ne more premakniti svoje že postavljene oznake ali postaviti svoje "
"oznake na že postavljeno oznako."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players cannot forfeit their turns."
msgstr "Igralci ne morejo izgubiti svojih potez."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Player who reaches five marks connected in a straight line (be it vertical, "
"horizontal or diagonal) wins the game."
msgstr ""
"Igralec, ki doseže pet točk, povezanih v ravno črto (navpično, vodoravno ali "
"diagonalno), zmaga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Tips"
msgstr "Nasveti za igro"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &bovo; is started the first time, it needs resizing. Resize the game "
"window to desired size, and &bovo; will scale up the playing board."
msgstr ""
"Ko se &bovo; zažene prvič, potrebuje spremembo velikosti. Spremenite "
"velikost okna igre na želeno velikost in &bovo; bo igralno ploščo povečal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first time &bovo; is started it is launched in demo mode, where two AI "
"players battle each other."
msgstr ""
"Ko se &bovo; prvič začne, se zažene v demo načinu, kjer se dva igralca AI "
"borita drug z drugim."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &bovo; is exited prior to game over, the active game is auto saved. If "
"&bovo; detects an auto saved game at startup, it is restored. If not, &bovo; "
"launches a demo mode."
msgstr ""
"Ko se &bovo; zapusti pred koncem igre, se aktivna igra samodejno shrani. Če "
"&bovo; ob zagonu zazna samodejno shranjeno igro, se obnovi. Če ne, &bovo; "
"zažene demo način."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can always start a new game with the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button "
"in the toolbar, the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu entry in the menubar or with the default "
"shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Novo igro lahko vedno začnete z gumbom <guibutton>Novo</guibutton> v orodni "
"vrstici, vnosom menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijsko vrstico ali s privzeto bližnjico "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a new game is started when a game is already active, it is counted as a "
"loss."
msgstr "Če se nova igra začne, ko je igra že aktivna, se šteje kot izgubljena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the difficulty can be done with the <guilabel>Difficulty</guilabel> "
"drop down box in the right end of the status bar, or from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Difficulty</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu entry in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Težavnost lahko spremenite s spustnim poljem <guilabel>Težavnost</guilabel> "
"na desnem koncu statusne vrstice ali v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Težavnost</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menijski vnos v "
"menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The effect of changing difficulty takes place immediately."
msgstr "Učinek spreminjanja težavnosti nastopi takoj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch the theme of &bovo; from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Theme</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu entry in the "
"menubar. The theme is then switched immediately."
msgstr ""
"Temo &bovo; iz vnosa menija lahko preklopite v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tema</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> v menijski vrstici. Tema se nato takoj preklopi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Animation can be switched on or off as you like from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Animation</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu entry in the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Animacijo lahko po želji vklopite ali izklopite v meniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Animacija</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you just realized you made a very bad move, you have the possibility to "
"undo your last move from the toolbar, the menubar or with the default undo "
"keyboard shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če ste pravkar ugotovili, da ste naredili zelo slabo potezo, imate možnost "
"razveljaviti svojo zadnjo potezo v orodni vrstici, menijski vrstici ali s "
"privzeto bližnjico na tipkovnici za razveljavitev <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap ></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can keep on undoing moves until you reaches the beginning of the game."
msgstr "Poteze lahko razveljavljate, dokler ne pridete do začetka igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't know what move to make, you can get a hint from the computer "
"player with the <guibutton>Hint</guibutton> button. The game piece suggested "
"by the &bovo; AI then flashes for a brief period of time."
msgstr ""
"Če ne veste, katero potezo narediti, lahko dobite namig od računalniškega "
"predvajalnika z gumbom <guibutton>Namig</guibutton>. Igralni del, ki ga "
"predlaga &bovo; AI nato za kratek čas utripa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a game is over, the <guibutton>Replay</guibutton> action is enabled, "
"which starts a replay of the last game."
msgstr ""
"Ko je igre konec, je omogočeno dejanje <guibutton>Ponovno predvajanje</"
"guibutton>, ki začne ponovitev zadnje igre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts a new game."
msgstr "Začne novo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Replay</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovna igra</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replay the last game."
msgstr "Ponovno odigrate zadnjo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting this item will end your current game, and exit &bovo;."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete ta element, boste končali trenutno igro in zapustili &bovo;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap> </keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap> </keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo the last move you made."
msgstr "Razveljavite zadnjo potezo, ki ste jo naredili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>H</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>H</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Namig</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Display</action> a hint for the next move. The game piece suggested "
"by the &bovo; AI then flashes for a brief period of time."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži</action> namig za naslednjo potezo. Igralni del, ki ga "
"predlaga &bovo; AI nato za kratek čas utripa."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Theme</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tema</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose one of the themes <guimenuitem>Scribble</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>High Contrast</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Spacy</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>Gomoku</guimenuitem> for the game."
msgstr ""
"Za igro izberite eno od tem <guimenuitem>Scribble</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Visoki kontrast</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Spacy</guimenuitem> "
"ali <guimenuitem>Gomoku</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Animation </guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Animacija </guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the animation on or off."
msgstr "Vklopite ali izklopite animacijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Težavnost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the game difficulty from various levels from "
"<guimenuitem>Ridiculously Easy</guimenuitem> up to <guimenuitem>Impossible</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite težavnost igre med različnimi stopnjami od <guimenuitem>Smešno "
"enostavne</guimenuitem> do <guimenuitem>Nemogoče</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &bovo; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &bovo; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change &bovo;'s visual theme you can use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Theme</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> menu entry on the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Da. Če želite spremeniti vizualno temo &bovo;, lahko uporabite menijski vnos "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tema</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> v menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje te igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. The game of &bovo; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ne. Igra &bovo; ni mogoče igrati s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No. There is no <quote>Save</quote> feature in &bovo; but &bovo; restores "
"the latest unfinished game on startup."
msgstr ""
"Ne. V &bovo; ni funkcije <quote>Shrani</quote>. ampak &bovo; obnovi zadnjo "
"nedokončano igro ob zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where are the highscores?"
msgstr "Kje so najboljši rezultati?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "&bovo; does not have this feature."
msgstr "&bovo; nima te funkcije."

